Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This game's winner is... \NHaneda Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. Isn't that Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,30,,{\fade(700,700)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad2\blur2\3c&H453265&\4c&H675E70&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H41&\fscx117\fscy88}Episode 8 \N {\fs96}Bewilderment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He is... my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Slotter's life is in fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you're not showing up \Ncarefree as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too concerned \Nabout why did your father abandon the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And is he really that vile a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But by a cruel irony, you ended up \Nfollowing the same path as the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Master? \NYou don't usually sigh that deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of strange, \NGinya is also acting a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't shown up here a single time recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What could have happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One's contents are vast \Nand cannot be filled with loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you try sustaining such a life, \Nthe hunger will bring you back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so... \NSo be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, it's about time I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been fate that drew us here, \Nwhat else can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like Big Bonus \Nhas suddenly been bestowed on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Because on my side it very much feels \Nlike an intentional calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've not been doing \Nenough exercises recently you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to burn a lot of subcutaneous fat. \NIs there a better place than a gym to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sole reason why I turned up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, it just turns out \NYuri is working here as well. Who would've thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Subcutaneous fat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Aren't you the most \Nrenowned instructor here, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one here is in a dire need of a coach. \NAren't we the mates by nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are bound to devote today to me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Is it intense enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not... yet. What's more important, \Nwhat are your plans for your next day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of talking, \Ntake a tighter grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... Yuri... \NIs your weekend schedule very tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your legs more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, to make your abdomen stronger, \Nyou have to raise your whole body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot thank you enough for today, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi... Are you feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Yuri's coaching \Nthat stunned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I should do something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to repay to you for that consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By the bayside, there's a pleasantly vibed restaurant \Nserving french cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless by any chance Yuri \Nprefers japanese cuisine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one place I'd like to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care to accompany me there, Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a second thought! \NI'll go wherever Yuri says!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the edge of the Earth or a cozy hotel - \Neverything is OK with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you can go wherever... \NBut you chose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! For the first time ever, \NI wanted to visit a parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressing buttons blindly won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. \NLet me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a lovely child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Instead, Yuri, \Ntry pressing them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The right timing decides everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch carefully on the spinning drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to notice big red Sevens as they are passing by. \NIt's easier once you get used.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now try to adjust to the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NNow just do the same with the right button.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more left. \NWatch closely as it spins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the timing for the Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tap... Tap... Tap... Hit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! \NThree Sevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did! \NDon't you think you have a hidden talent for it, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it distress me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, little Mai will also be living \Ntogether with us from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The time is ripe for us \Nto finally start being a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we have to part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you can be sure that mom \Nis always looking after you two from the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that day we have been raised \Nby our aunt and uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mom, which man is our real father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He never showed up - neither when Mai was born \Nnor when sister Sakura was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a vile man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was duly punished for abandoning you two. \NHe died too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It took no more than 3 months \Nafter my sister's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kojiro can in no way \Nbe considered a vile man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our piblings never ceased talking \Nabout how vile our father was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, in turn, claims \Nour father was a sound guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither strikes me as a person telling lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of work was he doing? What kind of father \Nhe was? I never had any chance to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing the aunt ever told me \Nis the most digestible one - that he was a vile man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, there's the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... \NWhere is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it with that punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My father might as well still be alive. \NAnd I... I'm alive, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I being such a laughing stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not taught to apologize \Nfor bumping into a person, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, \Nthe youth has no idea of decency these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed they don't! \NAt least look me in the eyes when I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You play pachislot with a deep hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba says... \Nhe can see that inside my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a punk! \NNow he is assaulting us without warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See what happens \Nwhen you underestimate a salaryman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever forget what a cruel place world is, \Nwe're here to remind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think he had his lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's unlikely apologizing, \Nso maybe we call it enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gutless scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who wants another drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess who decided to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Ginya \Nbe lying on the ground in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I applied all the treatment available. \NBut you still have to stay in bed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The hand is not injured, \Nthat matters the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, \Nyesterday I went on a date with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I saw Ginya \Nloafing by in the downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go find you later \Nto brag my accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I found you unconscious \Nin some backstreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you have lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't claim to know \Nwhat exactly is going on for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep it this way, \Nyou are bound to keep losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium does not tolerate such ineptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in your postbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely, a schedule for your next game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly \Nwhat Oumi would have said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One can see with a bare eye that fighting \Nin such condition will only lead to a beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The same pachislot \Nthat my dad has so much to do with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will no longer be fighting in Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's irrevocable since you decided so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my most precious rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a way, I don't want you \Nto get off the track that miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't show up today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder \Nwhat could have happened to that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,am going \Nessentially the same way my father once went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With pachislot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it so interesting about pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In pachislot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it this way \Nand you will lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best for everyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only way to end suffering. \NOnce and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell \Nam I doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. \NToday's game winner is Oumi Shunichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ginya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about Ginya, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, there is a good chance he doesn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not forgoing the hope. \NEither way, we can't do anything but watch how he copes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we make a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether Ginya shows up or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else do we come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To find out for certain, without guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we did, what would you bet on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dealer! \NIsn't it time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to come here another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting long enough. \NWell then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya understands that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you skip a prescheduled game \Nwithout particular reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A penalty follows - \Na complete reset of all of your previous progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You start from zero again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In worst cases, \None's license gets withdrawn completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, which answer are you going to give?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is wait. \NAfter all, we don't know the answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Game starts in 5 seconds. 4... 3... 2... 1... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come to Slothium in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Will you run away from the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that... The Otonashi guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he show up the last minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he was gonna come somehow, told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But can he really turn the tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this time he is determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad. \NI got lost, but I hope I'm not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot be terrified \Nby the sight of the machine forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At least for now, \NI should be able to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight my opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep fighting\Nbecause I have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
