Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boxer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NPro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will \Nstop the time.
